summary:
My name is Amanda Galiana and I am an 29 years old Architect from Spain graduated at Malaga's University with a degree in Architecture (M.Arch equivalent) in July 2014. 

Always interested in learning new softwares, I became in a BIM Methodology and 3D Visualization expert while developing my career of architecture. 

As an architect, I was working for four years in several architectural offices in Spain and The Netherlands, being part of teams led by experienced architects.
